Question 10
Write a function that takes an array of numbers and returns the sum. Use a loop.
lightbulb
Hint: Initialize total = 0, then loop and add each element.
function sumArray(arr) {
  let sum = 0;

  for (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
    sum += arr[i];
  }

  return sum;
}

console.log(sumArray([1, 2, 3, 4]));


